{"tid":527041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀][閪泰]理大教師熱狗鄭松泰被炒，正式通知不獲續約！","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T10:42:10.000Z","uid":49388,"like":77,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbd9ae6e1946cddc4630e2e7748e2db04fb52b4","tid":527041,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"【理大就倒旗案紀律聆訊有結果　鄭松泰：不獲續約】<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰去2016年10月在立法會大會上，將建制派放在會議廳的國旗區旗製品倒放，隨後被起訴侮辱國旗區旗罪並罪名成立，被罰款5000元。而在去年10月，鄭松泰收到所任教的理工大學通知，指就案件成立「紀律委員會」作跟進。鄭松泰今日（1月12日）表示，已收到校方的紀律裁決信，指鄭松泰在今年6月約滿後，不再續約。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰是在2017年10月13日收到理大通知，要成立「紀律委員會」就其倒旗案作跟進，理大當時交給他600多頁的文件，要求他就案件影響校譽、與教席關係等，作書面自辯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日李政熙上庭熱狗派人去搞人，今日到你地受Lu<br />\n閪人鄭松泰，抵撚死!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b384d2b5b9e8932b3f546363a47786e2c8e52b","tid":527041,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af84e6aa478c2b29e70ebe0920372e476dc786fc","tid":527041,"uid":39800,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/171111_50c81cfc695e097d25695bc74d7b3aaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F171111_50c81cfc695e097d25695bc74d7b3aaf.png&h=095ea3f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e9fb17b3d18649ab841b92033c0e57d433db59","tid":527041,"uid":14449,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":